PrecisAmendments to the GREAT LAKES PILOTAGE TARIFF REGULATIONS which increase the tariffs by 5.3% in International District No. 1 (including Lake Ontario), by 3.7% in International District No. 2 (west of the Welland Canal), and by 5% at the Port of Churchill.
